<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>xǔ duō gōng rén shī zōng 迦南499</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 xǔ duō gōng rén shī zōng, tān ài qián cái xū róng, zhǐ bù guò shì bǔ fēng zhuō yǐng.
 zhǔ ràng wǒ xīn sū xǐng, zhǔ ràng wǒ xīn sū xǐng, zài zhè gè shí dài sū xǐng,
 bàn yè yǒu xīn shì fā shēng, bàn yè yǒu xīn shì fā shēng, zhǔ a nǐ yǐn dǎo wǒ wǎng qián xíng.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>499</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
